# │ DEPLOYMENT NOTES                                                │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

# For Local Development:
# 1. Backend: Copy backend section to backend/.env
# 2. Frontend: Copy frontend section to .env.local
# 3. Start backend: cd backend && node src/index.js
# 4. Start frontend: npm run dev

# For Azure Deployment:
# 1. Update all localhost URLs to Azure URLs
# 2. Change NODE_ENV to production
# 3. Upload banking_private.pem to Azure
# 4. Configure App Service Application Settings with all variables
# 5. Enable "Allow Azure Services" in PostgreSQL firewall
# 6. Set HTTPS Only in App Service settings


